### Blog Public
# @name listPosts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/blog?limit=5&offset=0&sort=createdAt&order=desc

### Get by slug or id (replace :slugAfterCreate)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/blog/:slugAfterCreate

### Blog Admin
# @name getToken
GET http://localhost:3000/token

### Create post
# @name createPost
POST http://localhost:3000/api/blog/admin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{getToken.response.body.token}}

{
  "title": "Hello World",
  "excerpt": "Quick hello world post",
  "content": "This is a simple blog post for testing.",
  "author": "Admin",
  "tags": ["intro", "hello"],
  "videoUrl": null,
  "coverImage": null
}

### Update post (paste id from createPost)
# @name updatePost
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/blog/admin/{{createPost.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{getToken.response.body.token}}

{
  "excerpt": "Updated short summary",
  "tags": ["intro", "hello", "updated"]
}

### Delete post
# @name deletePost
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/blog/admin/{{createPost.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{getToken.response.body.token}}

### Bulk update
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/blog/admin/bulk/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{getToken.response.body.token}}

{
  "ids": ["{{createPost.response.body.id}}"],
  "updates": { "author": "System" }
}

### Bulk delete
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/blog/admin/bulk/delete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{getToken.response.body.token}}

{
  "ids": ["{{createPost.response.body.id}}"]
}
